item.title: CVE-2017-15719|2024-08-05T20:04:49.362Z -- apache%20software%20foundation -- wicket%20jquery%20ui
item.description: In Wicket jQuery UI 6.28.0 and earlier, 7.9.1 and earlier, and 8.0.0-M8 and earlier, a security issue has been discovered in the WYSIWYG editor that allows an attacker to submit arbitrary JS code to WYSIWYG editor.
